name: TUYUL
description:
tuyul is one of mythological creatures in indonesia.
they are mystical in nature and appear in the form of very small children (like leprechaun). they are mischievous and like to steal.
a lot of people in indonesia believe they truly exist (even in modern times such as nowadays). and due to tuyul's strong habit of thievery, some people keep them as pet to steal other's money and possession.
